Package: birdnetValidator
Title: Launch the BirdNET Validator App
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Benjamin", "Cretois", email = "benjamin.cretois@nina.no",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R wrapper for the BirdNET Validator Streamlit app. Installs the
    Python package automatically via reticulate and launches the validation
    interface in your browser. Ecologists can listen to audio clips and
    confirm or reject species identifications made by BirdNET.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.28)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 3.10)
